heroConfiguration.headline: Raptors cruise to 43-point rout of Spurs

gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Raptors 143, Spurs 100
gameRecap.subTitle: The Raptors defeated the Spurs, 143-100. Pascal Siakam led the way with a triple double, (22 points, 10 rebounds, 11 assists) while Gary Trent Jr. added 24 points in the victory. Keita Bates-Diop had tallied a team-high 17 points for the Spurs in the losing effort. The Raptors improve to 5-3 on the season, while the Spurs fall to 5-3.
